%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%

sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor EV as Evaluator
participant UI as Vendor Management UI
participant BFF as Vendor BFF
participant CACHE as Redis Cache
participant VMS as Vendor Management Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS Read schema"}

EV ->> UI: Open Vendor Management Home
UI ->> BFF: Get evaluator <br/>task queue

BFF ->> CACHE: Get evaluator queue cache
alt Cache Hit
    CACHE -->> BFF: Cached task queue
else Cache Miss
    BFF ->> VMS: getEvaluatorTasks(evaluatorId)
    VMS ->> READDB: GET assigned evaluation tasks
    VMS ->> READDB: GET and JOIN request header, <br/>vendor assignment, evaluation status
    READDB -->> VMS: Task list
    VMS -->> BFF: Evaluator queue
    BFF ->> CACHE: Cache evaluator queue
end

BFF -->> UI: Display Req ID, RFQ, Project, <br/>Stage, Evaluation Stage, Status
EV ->> UI: Click Perform Evaluation
UI -->> EV: Navigate to evaluation form